{"tid":676514,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[一支公遊記］奧地利 - Innsbuck 篇","createTime":"2018-05-24T12:13:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T14:13:59.000Z","uid":79662,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3be7b774145e839e63e4cc6e763ad71f7b4b6556","tid":676514,"uid":79662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T12:13:03.000Z","msg":"小弟前排去左奧地利 <br />\n由米蘭出發搭火車上<br />\n中途係一個唔多出名既小鎮訓左晚<br />\n依個小鎮叫 Innsbuck <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/195745_155d4229c9e3fae87f4ce185b3317a48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F195745_155d4229c9e3fae87f4ce185b3317a48.png&h=fb6fa99f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小弟留學都算成日出去窮遊 <br />\n但Innsbuck 比我感覺真係好小清新 <br />\n可能因為後面有排雪山做背景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/200026_d7cbb73e7714e3e66acf26ec98461a3e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F200026_d7cbb73e7714e3e66acf26ec98461a3e.png&h=1bfc0f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/200028_b385529d6bab5792ec20ea13ceb31dc5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F200028_b385529d6bab5792ec20ea13ceb31dc5.png&h=4c884b65&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/200030_9164ed424ed949b84c2bf661b9adf0da.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F200030_9164ed424ed949b84c2bf661b9adf0da.png&h=5d7e427f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實個鎮3-4個鍾係可以行哂<br />\n所以夜晚好少人 啲人好似NPC咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/200033_04a227dd3ebfcb182400123ad69da90c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F200033_04a227dd3ebfcb182400123ad69da90c.png&h=f7324228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朝早早左起身 <br />\n諗住可以係趕去下一個地點既火車之前上雪山睇下風景<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/200035_e14e6062791dc89131eef009ce9f3cb9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F200035_e14e6062791dc89131eef009ce9f3cb9.png&h=4eac57b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/200037_af00f0383a7fed7ebd7fea2e29ab3037.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F200037_af00f0383a7fed7ebd7fea2e29ab3037.png&h=7be5d9e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上山本來係因為車站係Zaha Hadid 設計 <br />\n諗住去朝聖下<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/200041_fffe9391f08b829226788f69040da139.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F200041_fffe9391f08b829226788f69040da139.png&h=19baaa33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果都係大自然比較吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後會去Salzburg -&gt; Hallstall -&gt; Wien -&gt; Prague"},{"pid":"6935bffd52728a8ddce427d13faa391356aa2595","tid":676514,"uid":84163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:46:06.000Z","msg":"見到個標題即刻入嚟！<br />\n我上年去過一次Innsbruck，好鍾意個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到你嘅行程諗起之前嘅歐遊trip，我都係去呢啲地方，好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你玩得開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127d5e6f1fe9ce300c69283f6519782958de1896","tid":676514,"uid":55664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T15:52:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11939ee590aeef28baddb13b7723a57cbc39f4fa","tid":676514,"uid